## Shooting drills
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tcoRi1OxFmo
1. Stationary Shot (10 Shots in Center, 1 Shot Each Corner R/L)
2. Roll to Shot (20 Shots on Frame R/L)
3. 10 yard Move to Shot (10 Moves/Shots R/L)
4. Corner of 18, Cut-In Curled Shot (10 Curled Shots Far Post R/L)
5. Back to Goal, Turn, Finessed Shot (10 Finessed Shots to Side Netting R/L)

