## Aggression & Protection drills
Tip: Use your entire body
Aggressive :  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oxHcnNdH4Ss
Protect / shield :
When ball is being passed to you and you have a defender by your side:
0. Get in front of the defender.
1. Close fist and bend knees.
2. Extend the arm, push the defender out and create your space.
3. Control the ball with outer foot.
4. Push with shoulders if needed.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vmuJwLGBlwU
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FtEMcmzdjrw

When you have the ball and dribbling:
1. Approach player with ball.
2. Spin and block the player (your back is on the player).
3. Dribble out
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LpDvue6qtzk

